| RISC OS ROM softload utility

| Set up environment, start the process...
Set File$Type_FE5 EPROM
Set SoftLoad$Dir <Obey$Dir>

| Prompt user if there are any ROM files...
| Possible optional parameters are -test -all
| See SoftLoad.!Help for details.
Run <SoftLoad$Dir>.Prompt %*0